@startuml sequence_zapping_exoplayer_v2
title Zapping - brodcast
' Open-source zamjena za Comedia. Plejer = ExoPlayer (androidx.media3, Apache-2.0).
' Sabloni: Module 5 Fig.3 (host stack), Module 6 Fig.4 (tune) i Fig.5 (A/V playback), Module 3 (PCR/PTS), Module 7 Fig.5 (zapping)
' Cuttlefish: izvor je TS fajl -> Media3 TsExtractor sam demuksuje PAT/PMT, vadi A/V/PCR (nije potreban poseban DTV MW)

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App" as App
  participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
end box
box "Open-source player - ExoPlayer / AndroidX Media3" #E8F5E9
  participant "ExoPlayer" as PLAYER
  participant "MediaSource / TsExtractor" as SRC
end box
box "Ispod plejera - Platform i HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "MediaCodec / AudioTrack" as AVDEC
end box

User -> App : Play channel 1
App -> TIS : onSetSurface(surface)
App -> TIS : onSetStreamVolume(0.0)
App -> TIS : onTune(channelUri)
note over TIS : channelUri -> TS izvor (file:///data/clear_0002.ts)\n+ ONID/TSID/SID procitani iz TV Provider-a
TIS -> PLAYER : new ExoPlayer.Builder(context).build()
TIS -> PLAYER : setVideoSurface(surface)
TIS -> PLAYER : addListener(playerListener)
TIS -> SRC : ProgressiveMediaSource.Factory(dataSource, DefaultExtractorsFactory)\n.createMediaSource(MediaItem.fromUri(tsUri))
SRC --> TIS : MediaSource
TIS -> PLAYER : setMediaSource(mediaSource)
TIS -> PLAYER : prepare()
note over PLAYER,SRC : prepare() je ASINHRON; izvor i dekoderi se postavljaju u pozadini\n(STATE_BUFFERING -> STATE_READY), app ceka event, ne pretpostavlja playback

PLAYER -> SRC : citaj TS + demuksuj (TsExtractor: PAT -> PMT -> A/V/PCR PID)
SRC --> PLAYER : track-ovi (video H.264, audio) + PTS timeline (PCR ref.)
PLAYER -> AVDEC : alociraj video (MediaCodec, AVC) + audio (AudioTrack); PTS/PCR A/V sync (lipsync)
note over AVDEC : demonstration: video+audio dekoder + display\nkomunicira sa HAL (VDEC/ADEC/GPU) (ref. Module 6 Fig.5; Module 3 PCR/PTS)
AVDEC --> PLAYER : A/V tece, sinhronizovano

TIS -> PLAYER : play()  (setPlayWhenReady(true))
PLAYER --> TIS : Player.Listener.onPlaybackStateChanged(STATE_READY)
PLAYER --> TIS : Player.Listener.onRenderedFirstFrame()
TIS -> App : notifyVideoAvailable() + unmute (restore volume)
TIS -> SRC : getCurrentTracks() / TvTrackInfo (ime, audio/titl)
SRC --> TIS : Tracks (video/audio/text)
TIS --> App : Service started -> Playback active

note over TUNERREF : za PRAVI RF tuner (ne file): android.media.tv.tuner.Tuner.tune(FrontendSettings)\n+ openFilter(...) hrane plejer; u Cuttlefish-u (file) ExoPlayer cita TS direktno
participant "(alt) Android Tuner Framework" as TUNERREF #DDDDDD
@enduml
